### Unused
Version 1.0

Use this useful utility tool to check what image resources are not being used in your Xcode projects.
Very useful to reduce your bundle size by showing you what images are not used!

![Unused Mac App](http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r1000/076/Purple/1a/6c/e8/mzl.uxykevec.800x500-75.jpg)

Created by Jeff Hodnett

jefers@gmail.com

http://www.twitter.com/jeffhodnett

http://www.jeffhodnett.com
name: Unused
tagline: A Mac app for checking Xcode projects for unused resources
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
